tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ProteinStructures (
  structure_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  structure_name VARCHAR(255),
  sequence TEXT,
  num_residues INTEGER
)

CREATE TABLE StructureAtoms (
    atom_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    structure_id INT,
    atom_name VARCHAR(255),
    atom_type VARCHAR(50),
    x_coord FLOAT,
    y_coord FLOAT,
    z_coord FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Residues (
    residue_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    atom_id INT,
    residue_name VARCHAR(3),
    chain_id CHAR,
    sequence_number INT
);

CREATE TABLE ProteinStructures (
    protein_id INT,
    protein_name VARCHAR(50),
    structure_data BLOB
)

CREATE TABLE AminoAcids (
    amino_acid_id INT,
    amino_acid_name VARCHAR(3),
    molecular_formula VARCHAR(10)
)

CREATE TABLE AtomCoordinates (
    atom_id INT,
    protein_id INT,
    amino_acid_id INT,
    x_coordinate FLOAT,
    y_coordinate FLOAT,
    z_coordinate FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Bonds (
    bond_id INT,
    atom_id1 INT,
    atom_id2 INT,
    bond_type VARCHAR(10)
)

CREATE TABLE StructuresMetadata (
    structure_id INT,
    description TEXT
)
